    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "S1和S3标为Infra_LoadBalancer，S2标为Infra_RedisCache。连接关系我画S1指向S3，S2也指向S3，表示汇聚到出口LB。",
