      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "PARSER这层复杂一些。P1是IngressController接收入口，P2是LoadBalancer做分发，P3是WorkerNode做核心解析，P4是另一个IngressController处理旁路流量。P2要同时连P3和P4。",
      "elements_involved": [
